26.1-25-16. Rebates prohibited - Exception.
1. No insurance producerAn insurance producer may not knowingly charge, demand, or receive
a premium for any insurance policy except in accordance with this chapter. No insurer or
employee of an insurer, and no insurance producer, broker or agent may pay, allow, or give, or
offer to pay, allow, or give, directly or indirectly, as an inducement to insurance, or after
